// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2157 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e41a3043-38e7-5b85-99aa-72d7b4d9ed91

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
